prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, crooked party hat, hanging upside-down from a tree branch and struggling comically to reach a slice of birthday cake that is dangling just out of its grasp from a string tied to the same branch. The sloth has a look of mild, humorous frustration on its face. Below the sloth, centered on the card, the words "happy belated-ish birthday" are written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is a flat 2D watercolor painting, featuring soft, pastel colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds around the edges of the sloth and cake, giving it a whimsical and handcrafted feel.
